#
# Test plans and (optionally) jobs unique to the Ubuntu Core and Classic devices.
#

id: oem-full
unit: test plan
_name: OEM - Full manual + automated OEM tests for Ubuntu Core and Classic
_description:
  Combined manual and automated test plans for Ubuntu Core and Classic devices.
include:
nested_part:
  oem-automated
  oem-manual
certification_status_overrides:
  apply blocker to .*

id: oem-automated
unit: test plan
_name: OEM - Automated only OEM tests for Ubuntu Core and Classic
_description:
  Ubuntu Core and Classic OEM test plan for the hardware. This test plan contains
  all of the automated tests used to validate the device.
estimated_duration: 120
include:
nested_part:
  oem-audio-automated
  oem-barcode-scanner-automated
  oem-bios-automated
  oem-bluetooth-automated
  oem-boot-automated
  oem-button-automated
  oem-buzzer-automated
  oem-camera-automated
